&CP2K
 PROGRAM      Quickstep
 PROJECT      H2O
 IOLEVEL      10
 FFTLIB       FFTSG
 RUN_TYPE     GEO_OPT
&END

&GEOOPT
 OPTIMIZER BFGS
 MAX_ITER  3
&END

&DFT
 FUNCTIONAL   Pade
&END

&QS
 CUTOFF       200
 EPS_DEFAULT  1.0E-4
&END

&SCF
 GUESS        ATOMIC
 EPS_SCF      1.0E-4
&END

&PRINT low
&END

&KIND H
 BASIS_SET    DZV-GTH-PADE
 POTENTIAL    GTH-PADE-q1
&END

&KIND O
 BASIS_SET    DZVP-GTH-PADE
 POTENTIAL    GTH-PADE-q6
&END

&CELL
 UNIT         ANGSTROM
 ABC          5.0  5.0  5.0
&END

&COORD
 O   0.000000    0.000000   -0.065587
 H   0.000000   -0.757136    0.520545
 H   0.000000    0.757136    0.520545
&END
